GULF OF GUINEA.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 25 FEB THRU 14 MAR BY
   M/V BGP PROSPECTOR TOWING TEN FOUR MILE
   LONG CABLES IN AREA BOUND BY
   04-05.9N 008-11.6E, 03-45.8N 008-37.7E,
   03-36.4N 008-31.1E, 03-57.0N 008-05.0E.
   WIDE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 240/14.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 15 MAR 14.
